{"tid":510428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"311補選應含淚投泛民定係投“另類選擇”?","createTime":"2017-12-26T13:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T15:02:55.000Z","uid":163916,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"333140334d3878456dc824ecb1925245006efb84","tid":510428,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"含淚投泛民當然是阻止保皇奪取議席的最直接方法，但缺點是繼續送錢畀泛民，泛民繼續壟斷政壇，不會反省己過。<br />\n<br />\n投&ldquo;另類選擇&rdquo;勝算當然不高，而且有可能令保皇贏出(有關害處，請看我舊帖。)<br />\n但有一點，其實一直被大家忽視，候選人其實每得一票，都有十幾蚊獎金(來自公帑)落袋。若你投了&ldquo;另類選擇&rdquo;，他就可以得到相應的財政支持。當然，你投泛民，你就會送錢畀泛民洗了。<br />\n不要輕視那十幾元，因為五萬票就是七十萬。<br />\n<br />\n你一票的力量，其實不只表態咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n舊帖：一齊分析311泛民贏唔返分組否決權嘅後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/507705/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/507705/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"84129818bd9ae3464d6fde8468cae4e4f092e465","tid":510428,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T08:18:26.000Z","msg":"冇人想理?"},{"pid":"6259a88b9c93bc0f626f74dcafb486a667751032","tid":510428,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:10:28.000Z","msg":"大家又係時候含撚投泛民喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a0b4d80b611153380c0b2eab03cba66bd1d560","tid":510428,"uid":164419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"447e5866cb8154c5249bd43f8874c544c5e981b3","tid":510428,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"唔投 徙時間"},{"pid":"607db07dbc30db664378d3f49dd6cc642d55d893","tid":510428,"uid":148639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}